              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "7Be isotope was generated by means of the one proton",
                "transfer reaction 3He (6Li,7Be). Mixed secondary beam",
                "consisting of 8B, 7Be, and 6Li with rates of",
                "0.5-1.2E+5 particles/s were produced using primary",
                "6Li3+ beams  with energies between 31 and 38 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
